If your community data update fails, it may be that the network in your area cannot connect to Github. You can try to download FastGithub or hang an agent to solve it;
If your market data update fails, please confirm whether you you can open https://warframe.market. If you cannot open it, please refer to Github's handling method to solve it through a network proxy. 
But after set proxy, the UWP application may not be able to access the network, this problem will provide a solution in the application's Github homepage
